<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9344</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14161</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪跳着去儿童中心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14161</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呱、呱、呱。” 她呱呱叫着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在想自己的青蛙，呱呱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>呱呱今天在兽医那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪走进体育馆，雪莉老师吹了吹哨子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43229</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“该出去了！” 老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我们要玩儿跳房子。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51401</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她已经在地上画好了格子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51401</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57614</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪蹦蹦跳跳。“我们要像呱呱一样跳！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57614</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “我们不只是跳。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是一个特别的跳房子游戏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65534</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们要在每一个格子里写一种动作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70215</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果你跳到了那个格子，就要完成格子里写的动作。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要写什么样的动作呢？” 尼娜问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有趣的就行。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“比如说，做十个开合跳！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“或者五个俯卧撑？” 波比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92334</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“或者转八个圈？” 贾森问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没错！” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105544</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拿粉笔开始写吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105544</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪开心地写着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都写好了，他们在雪莉老师身后排好队。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师拿起一个沙包。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122957</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“先把沙包扔到一个格子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122957</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>单脚跳格子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128726</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>踩到线，就出局！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132881</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>跳到格子里之后，就做格子里写的动作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132881</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137609</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果你完成不了那个动作，也出局。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137609</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142907</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我先来！” 莉琪马上说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142907</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪扔出沙包。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她跳到沙包掉下的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“六个俯卧撑。” 她念道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157208</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是我写的！” 波比自豪地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一、二、三、四、五、六。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 莉琪做俯卧撑，大家帮她数数。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168408</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“耶！” 尼娜欢呼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>下一个是她。她跳到格子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“五个青蛙跳？这肯定是你写的，莉琪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185689</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>什么是青蛙跳？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185689</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190462</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪咯咯笑。“就是像呱呱一样跳！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190462</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她蹲下来，往前跳。“就像这样！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜脸红了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一定要做吗？” 她问雪莉老师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204444</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师点点头。“这是游戏的一部分。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要不然你就出局了。” 伊坦说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这么做会给青蛙带来好运。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220989</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家看着莉琪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223663</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真的吗？” 贾森问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223663</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227156</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得是。” 莉琪回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227156</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232477</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜叹了口气，做了五个青蛙跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232477</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“耶！太棒了！” 莉琪欢呼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241491</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>下一个是伊坦。他需要做一个侧手翻。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比转了十圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森学螃蟹走了一分钟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252342</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他们每个人玩儿了一轮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252342</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快就该回室内了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261908</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呱呱怎么样？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261908</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264114</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪低下头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他在兽医那里，他不吃东西。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275140</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“莉琪，这真糟糕。希望他没事。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275140</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪点点头。“我也希望他没事。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，莉琪的妈妈来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈！” 莉琪大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291881</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“宝贝，有好消息。呱呱今天吃了五只虫子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291881</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一切都很好！” 妈妈开心地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295958</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪跳起来，拥抱了尼娜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“青蛙跳真的带来了好运！谢谢你，尼娜。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>